Magpie
```json
{
  "application": "Magpie",
  "software": [
    {
      "name": "Spark",
      "version": "3.0.3-bin-hadoop3.2",
      "setup_type": "STANDALONE",
      "home": "${HOME}/spark-${SPARK_VERSION}",
      "local_dir": "/tmp/${USER}/spark",
      "worker_cores_per_node": "8 (default)",
      "worker_memory_per_node": "16000M (default)",
      "worker_directory": "/tmp/${USER}/spark/work (default)",
      "job_memory": "2048M (default)",
      "driver_memory": "2048M (default)",
      "daemon_heap_max": "2000M (default)",
      "environment_extra_path": "${HOME}/spark-my-environment (default)",
      "job": "sparkpi (default)",
      "default_parallelism": "8 (default)",
      "memory_fraction": "0.6 (default)",
      "memory_storage_fraction": "0.5 (default)",
      "storage_memory_fraction": "0.6 (default)",
      "shuffle_memory_fraction": "0.2 (default)",
      "rdd_compress": "true (default)",
      "io_compression_codec": "lz4 (default)",
      "deploy_spreadout": "true (default)",
      "job_classpath": "",
      "job_library_path": "",
      "job_java_opts": "",
      "local_scratch_dir": "/lustre/${USER}/sparkscratch/",
      "local_scratch_dir_clear": "yes (default)",
      "network_timeout": "120 (default)",
      "yarn_staging_dir": "file:///lustre/${USER}/sparkStaging/ (default)",
      "sparkpi_slices": "4 (default)"
    },
    {
      "name": "Alluxio",
      "version": "2.3.0",
      "home": "${HOME}/alluxio-${ALLUXIO_VERSION}",
      "local_dir": "/tmp/${USER}/alluxio",
      "worker_on_master": "yes (default)",
      "under_fs_dir": "/lustre/${USER}/alluxio",
      "data_clear": "yes (default)",
      "worker_memory_size": "16GB",
      "worker_tier0_path": "/mnt/ramdisk",
      "ramfs_mount_option": "SudoMount (default)",
      "read_type": "CACHE (default)",
      "write_type": "CACHE_THROUGH (default)",
      "job": "testalluxio (default)"
    },
    {
      "name": "Hadoop",
      "setup_type": "MR or YARN (required for Spark YARN)"
    }
  ],
  "resource_requirements": [
    {
      "name": "nodes",
      "description": "Node count should include one node for the head/management/master node. For example, if you want 8 compute nodes to process data, specify 9 nodes below. If including Zookeeper, include expected Zookeeper nodes. For example, if you want 8 Hadoop compute nodes and 3 Zookeeper nodes, specify 12 nodes (1 master, 8 Hadoop, 3 Zookeeper). Also take into account additional nodes needed for other services."
    },
    {
      "name": "time",
      "description": "Note defaults of MAGPIE_STARTUP_TIME & MAGPIE_SHUTDOWN_TIME, this timelimit should be a fair amount larger than them combined."
    },
    {
      "name": "job_name",
      "description": "This will be used in naming directories for the job."
    },
    {
      "name": "partition",
      "description": "Partition to launch job in."
    }
  ]
}
```
